; Fixture journal for /api/credit-cards integration tests.
; Designed to exercise:
;   - two card accounts under DIFFERENT prefix forms (cartão and credit-card)
;   - one card with `; alias:` directive (Q4 path c) and one without (path b)
;   - one active installment from 5 months ago (TV 6x → 1 month live)
;   - one finished installment from ~2 years ago (OLD 6x → completed)
;   - one refund on the credit-card side (Q3: positive expense-side reduces)
;   - a normal purchase on each card
;   - a card payment (assets → liability) that must NOT count as spend
;   - a dormant card (zero balance + zero monthly spend) → excluded
;
; "Today" for tests is fixed via dependency injection; the dates here are
; chosen so a today around 2026-04-15 hits all the desired states:
;   - TV purchased 2025-11-01 + 6 months = 2026-05-01 ≥ 2026-04-15 → LIVE
;   - OLD purchased 2024-04-01 + 6 months = 2024-10-01 < 2026-04-15 → done
;
; Account directives WITH and WITHOUT alias on purpose.

account liabilities:cartão:nubank          ; alias: Nubank Lucas
account liabilities:credit-card:visa
account liabilities:cartão:dormente
account assets:bank
account income:salary
account expenses:groceries
account expenses:dining
account expenses:moradia:equipamentos
account expenses:other

2026-01-01 * Opening
    assets:bank                         5000.00
    equity:opening

; ── Active installment (5 months ago, 6x → still 1 month live).
2025-11-01 * ELECTROLUX TV
    expenses:moradia:equipamentos       1800.00  ; parcelamento: TV 6x
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

; ── Completed installment (April 2024, 6x → done by Oct 2024).
2024-04-01 * Old fridge
    expenses:moradia:equipamentos        900.00  ; parcelamento: OLD 6x
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

; ── Normal April purchases on each card.
2026-04-05 * Supermarket on Nubank
    expenses:groceries                   200.00
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

2026-04-10 * Restaurant on Visa
    expenses:dining                      150.00
    liabilities:credit-card:visa

; ── Refund on Nubank in April (positive expense-side amount).
2026-04-12 * Refund of groceries
    expenses:groceries                   -50.00
    liabilities:cartão:nubank

; ── Payment of the Visa invoice (must NOT show up as spend).
2026-04-20 * Pagamento Visa
    assets:bank                         -100.00
    liabilities:credit-card:visa
